{"tid":2479322,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一路向西-男主角-張建聲喺無限斜棟入面又幾好戲","createTime":"2021-04-07T17:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T23:14:12.000Z","uid":38177,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d26af1daed843518209ec4bcb856b4d954357c5c","tid":2479322,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T17:48:58.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇吓viu套新劇<br />\n<br />\n睇到個男二做黑警即刻唔想睇<br />\n<br />\n但見到個死黑警比上頭撚到成隻死狗咁又幾過癮<br />\n<br />\n女主角正面抽擊死黑警&rdquo;叫你行就行，企就企&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到黑警𥚃外不是人，真係夠哂寫實，貼地<br />\n<br />\n個黑警上司嗰種公器私用，黑人憎到仆街，仲以為係啲不嬲都係做黑人憎角色既老戲骨演<br />\n<br />\n睇真啲，<span class=\"x-large\">仆你個街，一路向西個男主角黎架喂</span><br />\n<br />\n真係做戇鳩直男又得，黑人憎死黑警又得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYknxqdQ21az6N91PLqrdff8U5asMitUDpaRFXU6QBD1d?filename=azr7pcr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fazr7pcr.jpg&h=70352fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://viu.tv/encore/generation-slash\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fviu.tv%2Fencore%2Fgeneration-slash&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYaEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=382d64b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://viu.tv/encore/generation-slash</a>"},{"pid":"8930af6c3dd60df2119b11e1420456bce48430d1","tid":2479322,"uid":38177,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T17:51:11.000Z","msg":"許腎同豪仔做編劇真係唔會令人失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cdf68ae729a501fe68990fcc8ba4ed69e8a41a2","tid":2479322,"uid":38177,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T17:53:42.000Z","msg":"最緊要係選角選得好，出嗰兩集，啲戲搶到成套戲比佢搶哂，張建聲喺茶水間撚鳩男二嗰幕真係又搶戲又寫實，反而男二成碌木企喺度，交唔到戲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de977029a1b974137575b8decb577e43c0897ac1","tid":2479322,"uid":96704,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:08:44.000Z","msg":"張建聲不嬲都幾好